      "date": "2019-02-25 17:35:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review+1\n\n(2 comments)\n\nProbably the next step here would be to change the MDS mirror selection code to prefer a mirror that is non-rotational over one that isn't. We don't want to change the OST allocation policy to do that, or the flash OSTs would fill quickly, but if there is a mirrored file that is allocated over different OST types, then we may as well default to writing to the flash mirror.",
